13
00:02:00.954 --> 00:02:02.539
Tell 'em that's the last of it.

14
00:02:03.373 --> 00:02:05.876
<i>State your name
and new position.</i>

15
00:02:07.044 --> 00:02:08.418
Lukas Kyle.

16
00:02:08.419 --> 00:02:10.047
IT shadow.

17
00:02:11.173 --> 00:02:13.592
<i>Verified. Welcome. Lukas Kyle.</i>

18
00:02:14.885 --> 00:02:16.428
The living quarters
are that way.

19
00:02:17.179 --> 00:02:19.305
You will live here while
you familiarize yourself

20
00:02:19.306 --> 00:02:21.057
